{"id":2252,"date":"2024-07-13T21:42:24","date_gmt":"2024-07-13T21:42:24","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/yannichau.i234.me\/?p=2252"},"modified":"2024-12-16T22:27:27","modified_gmt":"2024-12-16T22:27:27","slug":"photopoems-4-a-sun-clouds-hills-and-a-bridge-of-thoughts","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/2024\/07\/13\/2252","title":{"rendered":"Photopoems 4: A sun, clouds, hills and a bridge of thoughts"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large wp-duotone-grayscale\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" src=\"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/IMG_5406-1024x640.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2277\" srcset=\"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/IMG_5406-1024x640.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/IMG_5406-300x188.jpg 300w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/IMG_5406-768x480.jpg 768w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/IMG_5406-1536x960.jpg 1536w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/IMG_5406-2048x1280.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\"><strong>The Sun<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Like a timid introvert<br>Hiding behind the mountains<br>Gently peeking through the misty skirts<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Awake!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Like drops of smearing paint<br>She blushes the entire canvas with tangerine streaks<br>Caressing the clouds with light medallion taints<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Rise!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Like a brave, glowing flame<br>Her vibrancy came<br>Popping<br>Sizzling<br>Crackling<br>Frizzling<br>Filling the rifts with beaming scorching rays.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Rejoice!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Like an ephemeral thriller<br>Her magical glee vasnishes from sight<br>As she reveals the charming azure that stays.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-17-1024x768.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2280\" srcset=\"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-17-1024x768.png 1024w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-17-300x225.png 300w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-17-768x576.png 768w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-17-1536x1153.png 1536w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-17-2048x1537.png 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\"><strong>Clouds<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Caressing, gently, the<br>Lavish, immaculately white snow<br>On the<br>Utterly almighty Annapurnas, as I gaze upon it,<br>Dumbfounded and simply amazed!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large wp-duotone-grayscale\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-3-1024x683.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2237\" srcset=\"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-3-1024x683.png 1024w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-3-300x200.png 300w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-3-768x512.png 768w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-3-1536x1024.png 1536w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-3.png 1897w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\"><strong>Terraced Gardens<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Rows<br>alternating<br>highlights and<br>shadows gleaming<br>under the exuberant sun<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Jagged<br>and uneven<br>overloaded with<br>the benevolance of<br>farmers\u2019 tender footsteps<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Steps<br>leading to<br>the azure blue<br>stpes descending<br>from what we call heaven<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large wp-duotone-grayscale\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"817\" height=\"1024\" src=\"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-15-817x1024.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2250\" srcset=\"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-15-817x1024.png 817w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-15-239x300.png 239w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-15-768x963.png 768w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-15-1225x1536.png 1225w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-15.png 1521w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 817px) 100vw, 817px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\"><strong>Bridge of thoughts<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">While I cross a cantilever bridge that<br>leaps<br>across the<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">deep<br>deep<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">valley<br>as I ponder upon my<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">deep<br>deep <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">thoughts.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The Sun Like a timid introvertHiding behind the mountainsGently peeking through the misty skirts Awake! Like drops of smearing paintShe blushes the entire canvas with tangerine streaksCaressing the clouds with light medallion taints Rise! Like a brave, glowing flameHer vibrancy camePoppingSizzlingCracklingFrizzlingFilling the rifts with beaming scorching rays. Rejoice! Like an ephemeral thrillerHer magical glee vasnishes [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":2280,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[5,54,8,1],"tags":[61,60,17,51],"class_list":["post-2252","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-photography","category-photopoems","category-travel","category-uncategorized","tag-annapurna","tag-nepal","tag-photography","tag-photopoems"],"acf":[],"featured_media_src_url":"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-17-1024x768.png","_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2252","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2252"}],"version-history":[{"count":7,"href":"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2252\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2284,"href":"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\